<br>
It appears that <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Magicians</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> for a brief time have the attention of <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Verant</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  Just as you have, we seek some remedies for our perceived greivances.<br>
<br>
One important idea that has gained significant support among <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Magicians</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is called <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Indifferent Summoned Pets</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<br>
<br>
The basic argument goes that bad pathing prevents <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Magicians</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> from using pets in many places without an unacceptable level of risk, especially in raids.  By making pets <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>indifferent</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, these risks are minimized, and <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Magicians</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> can use their already existing strength in places that had relegated them to second class citizenship.  It would allow for greater participation in raids by <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Magicians</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, without directly increasing their firepower.  We believe that the other penalties and costs associated with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Elementals</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> are sufficiently balancing.<br>
<br>
The problem is that this is a radical proposal, and will likely have unintended consequences.  We would like <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>your</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> help in brainstorming the consequences, especially exploits.  To date, no significant unintended consequence or exploit has been discovered, but I am certain we have not exhausted the possibilities.<br>
<br>
The original discussion in the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Magician Class Balance Forum</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is found here: <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessage?topicID=63.topic">Brainstorm Consequences of Indifferent Pets</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br>
<br>
Please apply your fiendishness and cunning to this possible change.<br>
<br>
Yours in casting,<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Razamatazz Pizzazz</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Mage of a Thousand Words, and Abuser of EZCodes<br>
